text: Suka van Gurp (born 1994) is a Dutch softball player. She plays with Sparks Haarlem. She is member of the Netherlands women's national softball team. With the national team she became European champion at the 2022 Women's Softball European Championship. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch softball players Category:Sportswomen
